ed_route:\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\"`, status, focus, findingsCount, newInfoRatio, noveltyJustification, keyQuestions, answeredQuestions, ruledOut, toolsUsed, sourcesQueried, timestamp, durationMs, sessionId `fanout-sol-high-fast-1784623934648-kt3qkt`, generation 1, executor `{ \"kind\":\"cli-opencode\", \"model\":\"openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\" }`, and optional graphEvents.\n+- The narrative must contain Focus, Actions Taken, Findings, Questions Answered, Questions Remaining, Ruled Out, Dead Ends, Sources Consulted, Assessment, Reflection, and Recommended Next Focus.\n+- Verify all three artifacts and exact one-record append before returning.\n+\n+## ITERATION OBJECTIVE\n+\n+Produce a forensic baseline, not generic recommendations. Identify what each current command body literally says, what its presentation asset contributes, what the shared contract centralizes, which parts of the 002 literal templates were implemented indirectly, and which qualities still must become visible literal command text. End with the narrowest productive focus for iteration 2.\n","additions":56,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/004-commands/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/prompts/iteration-001.md","time":{"start":1784624298621,"end":1784624298625}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0f797809dddc4f14016a5f348fca5c819199330225791542c7"}},"id":"prt_f83e55217001TmpEalS92C636u","sessionID":"ses_07c1fcf6effe2YUDoq6jbB4HYf","messageID":"msg_f83e52a02001uV3xgFZ6eB62RJ"}}
