ement progressive intake and visible lifecycle blocks but fragment prompt wording away from command bodies.\"},\n+    {\"id\":\"I001-F4\",\"iteration\":1,\"summary\":\"The skill-local creation contract centralizes choreography and authority while intentionally excluding design taste.\"},\n+    {\"id\":\"I001-F5\",\"iteration\":1,\"summary\":\"The remaining gap is an evocative, actionable, command-visible creation brief, not missing routing architecture.\"}\n+  ],\n+  \"ruledOutDirections\": [\n+    \"Replace the working routers wholesale\",\n+    \"Copy mode-owned taste doctrine into commands\",\n+    \"Treat presentation assets or the shared contract alone as the literal-prompt deliverable\"\n+  ],\n   \"metrics\": {\n-    \"iterationsCompleted\": 0,\n-    \"openQuestions\": 5,\n-    \"resolvedQuestions\": 0,\n-    \"keyFindings\": 0,\n-    \"convergenceScore\": 0,\n-    \"coverageBySources\": {}\n-  }\n+    \"iterationsCompleted\": 1,\n+    \"openQuestions\": 4,\n+    \"resolvedQuestions\": 1,\n+    \"keyFindings\": 5,\n+    \"convergenceScore\": 0.1,\n+    \"coverageBySources\": {\"commands\":5,\"presentations\":5,\"shared-contract\":1,\"prior-research\":2}\n+  },\n+  \"status\": \"iterating\",\n+  \"sessionId\": \"fanout-sol-high-fast-1784623934648-kt3qkt\",\n+  \"generation\": 1,\n+  \"lastUpdated\": \"2026-07-21T08:59:21Z\"\n }\n","additions":32,"deletions":11},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-research/.opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/004-commands/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/deep-research-state.jsonl","relativePath":".opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/004-commands/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/deep-research-state.jsonl","type":"update","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0093-sk-design-012-gap-re