ml:21-33\"]}\n5: {\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"I004-F4\",\"iteration\":4,\"summary\":\"Audit remains review-only; md-generator alone may write artifacts and only measured values may enter token tables.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/SKILL.md:166-175\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/SKILL.md:242-274\"]}\n6: {\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"I004-F5\",\"iteration\":4,\"summary\":\"Safe shipment requires an include-root live fixture, test-first body invariants, atomic package ownership edits, and suffix/status/mutation negative cases.\",\"sources\":[\".opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/scripts/interface-command-contract.test.mjs:28-139\",\".opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/scripts/design-command-surface-check.test.mjs:31-191\",\"https://opencode.ai/docs/commands/#file-references\"]}\n7: {\"type\":\"observation\",\"iteration\":4,\"summary\":\"Current command contract baseline passed 15 of 15 Node tests with zero failures.\",\"sources\":[\"command output: node --test .opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/scripts/interface-command-contract.test.mjs .opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/scripts/design-command-surface-check.test.mjs\"]}\n8: {\"type\":\"observation\",\"iteration\":4,\"summary\":\"Official docs prove @ file-content inclusion but do not explicitly prove the project-root base of @./.opencode/...; a live fixture remains required.\",\"sources\":[\"https://opencode.ai/docs/commands/#file-references\"]}\n\n(End of file - total 8 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":4,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\",\"run\":4,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Adversarial conformance review and corrections to the five iteration-3 body cores\",\"findingsCount\":5,\"newInfoRatio\":1.0,\"noveltyJustification\":\"4 of 5 findings were fully new and 1 partially new (0.90), plu