lude Resolution, Final Corrected Grammar, Acceptance Matrix, Rollout and Rollback, Questions Answered, Open Implementation Detail, Eliminated Alternatives, Sources Consulted, Assessment, Reflection, Synthesis Handoff.\n+- Verify all artifacts and boundary before return.\n+\n+## ITERATION OBJECTIVE\n+\n+Close the forced five-iteration loop with implementation-grade synthesis inputs. Preserve uncertainty only where the lineage-only boundary prevents the confirming live fixture; make every other deliverable concrete and testable.\n","additions":51,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/007-gap-remediation-research/004-commands/research/lineages/sol-high-fast/prompts/iteration-005.md","time":{"start":1784626155201,"end":1784626155212}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_061a9364b2182851016a5f3bcecd5c8199905d31888a0cc57f"}},"id":"prt_f8401a0150017vS2gythwX4cME","sessionID":"ses_07c1fcf6effe2YUDoq6jbB4HYf","messageID":"msg_f84018cb8001wQETEDceO2ttO3"}}
