{"type":"text","timestamp":1784626754220,"sessionID":"ses_07c1fcf6effe2YUDoq6jbB4HYf","part":{"id":"prt_f840b306c001a8RsrX0fK1y8wh","messageID":"msg_f840b1a9f001J55sukDnOjib1X","sessionID":"ses_07c1fcf6effe2YUDoq6jbB4HYf","type":"text","text":"Final integrity checks passed, but the owner-scoped lock release returned `released:false`; the lock is stale because its 5-minute heartbeat expired during the forced run. I’m using the lock CLI’s recovery contract rather than deleting the sentinel manually.","time":{"start":1784626753644,"end":1784626754217},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0f423c6d859c797d016a5f3e419af4819181be51d8e59badc4","phase":"commentary"}}}}
